info.text: How do I create an Instagram account?
Instagram app for Android and iPhone:
Download the Instagram app from the
Once the app is installed, tap
Sign Up With Email or Phone Number
(iPhone), then enter your email address or phone number (which will require a confirmation code) and tap
to sign up with your Facebook account.
If you register with your email or phone number,
and password, fill out your profile info and then tap
. If you register with Facebook, you'll be prompted to log into your Facebook account if you're currently logged out.

If you sign up with email, make sure you enter your email address correctly and choose an email address that only you can access. If you log out and forget your password, you'll need to be able to access your email to get back into your Instagram account.
Note that if you created your account recently, people on Instagram may see that you have a new account.
